column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, #) as SpecobjId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq (up_ra, up_dec, #) IS NOT # EXEC spExecuteSQL ' SELECT u.up_name as [name], s.specobjid, s.ra, s.dec, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.scienceprimary, s.bestobjid, s.fluxobjid, s.targetobjid FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN SpecObj s ON s.specObjID = x.specObjID
